file: crates/ctx-verify/src/error.rs
behavior: Defines the CheckError enum, the single error taxonomy used across ctx-verify for tool-invocation and report-output failures.
edit_notes:
  - Variant set is consumed by report-encoding and tool-runner call sites elsewhere in the crate; adding/renaming variants requires updating those match sites.
functions:
invariants:
  - Each variant carries only String-based context (tool name/detail), no source error chaining via #[from] or #[source].
external_deps:
  - thiserror: derives Display/Error impls from the #[error(...)] format strings.